log
@Initial import of FreeBSD sort.
@
text
@/*	$OpenBSD: fsort.h,v 1.10 2007/03/13 17:33:58 millert Exp $	*/

/*-
 * Copyright (c) 1993
 *	The Regents of the University of California.  All rights reserved.
